{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Est-ce que c'est la solution pour vous, le nucl\u00e9aire?", "start": 0.2, "duration": 2.733}, {"text": "C'\u00e9tait une erreur d'en sortir ?", "start": 2.933, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "C'\u00e9tait \u00e9videmment", "start": 4.933, "duration": 0.883}, {"text": "une folie d'en sortir !", "start": 5.816, "duration": 0.984}, {"text": "Le nucl\u00e9aire", "start": 6.8, "duration": 0.483}, {"text": "n'est pas une solution de long terme, peut-\u00eatre.", "start": 7.283, "duration": 2.017}, {"text": "Il faut continuer \u00e0 chercher", "start": 9.3, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "pour trouver d'autres sources d'\u00e9nergie", "start": 10.316, "duration": 1.517}, {"text": "qui n'impliquent pas les m\u00eames risques.", "start": 11.833, "duration": 1.983}, {"text": "Je ne dis pas qu'il", "start": 13.816, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "n'y a pas de risque nucl\u00e9aire.", "start": 14.516, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "Mais la v\u00e9rit\u00e9,", "start": 15.9, "duration": 0.883}, {"text": "c'est que le nucl\u00e9aire, c'est l'\u00e9nergie", "start": 16.783, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "qui a fait le moins de morts dans l'histoire,", "start": 17.816, "duration": 1.734}, {"text": "contrairement au charbon", "start": 19.55, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "qui tue tous les ans", "start": 20.516, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "des milliers de personnes,", "start": 21.383, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "y compris en France.", "start": 22.166, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "Contrairement au gaz.", "start": 23.116, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "Il faut absolument", "start": 24.683, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "arr\u00eater avec ce d\u00e9lire.", "start": 25.733, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "Et je crois que le nucl\u00e9aire", "start": 26.5, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "est le sympt\u00f4me de l'hypocrisie", "start": 27.566, "duration": 1.85}, {"text": "de nos \u00e9cologistes.", "start": 29.416, "duration": 0.884}, {"text": "Je le dis tr\u00e8s simplement : la v\u00e9rit\u00e9", "start": 30.3, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "c'est que,", "start": 32.066, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "en r\u00e9alit\u00e9,", "start": 32.716, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "derri\u00e8re ce combat contre le nucl\u00e9aire,", "start": 33.65, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "il y a un combat contre", "start": 35.083, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "la consommation,", "start": 36.35, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "contre le capitalisme,", "start": 37.066, "duration": 1.034}, {"text": "contre l'\u00e9conomie de march\u00e9.", "start": 38.1, "duration": 1.183}, {"text": "Je comprends ce combat-l\u00e0,", "start": 39.283, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "mais en fait,", "start": 40.433, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "il ne faut plus nous faire croire", "start": 41.033, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "que vous voulez sauver le climat.", "start": 42.383, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "Parce que si on veut sauver le climat,", "start": 43.583, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "on n'a pas le droit", "start": 45.116, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "de tirer sur l'\u00e9nergie", "start": 45.833, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "la plus d\u00e9carbon\u00e9e qui soit !", "start": 46.766, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "Et aujourd'hui,", "start": 48.033, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "la v\u00e9rit\u00e9", "start": 48.8, "duration": 0.516}, {"text": "c'est que si on prend au s\u00e9rieux", "start": 49.316, "duration": 1.284}, {"text": "le risque environnemental r\u00e9el,", "start": 50.6, "duration": 1.866}, {"text": "alors oui, je le dis, un jour,", "start": 52.466, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "on attaquera -", "start": 54.3, "duration": 0.583}, {"text": "je sais que c'est votre grande cause", "start": 54.883, "duration": 1.183}, {"text": "- pour \"\u00e9cocide\"", "start": 56.066, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "ceux qui nous ont contraints", "start": 57.233, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "\u00e0 retourner \u00e0 des \u00e9nergies polluantes.", "start": 58.966, "duration": 1.917}, {"text": "Qui pollue aujourd'hui", "start": 60.883, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "le plus en Europe ?", "start": 62.45, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "Ce sont les pays qui ont d\u00e9cid\u00e9", "start": 63.533, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "de sortir du nucl\u00e9aire.", "start": 64.933, "duration": 0.583}, {"text": "Et qui, aujourd'hui,", "start": 65.516, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "nous met en danger,", "start": 66.35, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "y compris sur le plan social,", "start": 67.433, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "y compris sur le plan \u00e9conomique ?", "start": 68.966, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "Eh bien,", "start": 70.066, "duration": 0.4}, {"text": "ce sont ceux qui continuent", "start": 70.466, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "d'alimenter cette id\u00e9ologie,", "start": 71.816, "duration": 0.884}, {"text": "qui n'est pas fond\u00e9e sur des faits,", "start": 72.7, "duration": 1.666}, {"text": "qui est fond\u00e9e sur", "start": 74.366, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "de la propagande de bas \u00e9tage.", "start": 75.133, "duration": 2.583}, {"text": "La question des cours d'eau, pardon,", "start": 77.716, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "mais c'est de la propagande", "start": 78.433, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "compl\u00e8tement aberrante.", "start": 79.383, "duration": 0.95}]}